{"tid":100498,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生　兜兜轉轉遊蕩半生","createTime":"2017-01-30T05:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T06:26:03.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2861668a2b4e8474d7461ce18c368afe6da15b4","tid":100498,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:38:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HucAUIE4gTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHucAUIE4gTs&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxskjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=e35ce226\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HucAUIE4gTs</a><br />\n<br />\n人生　兜兜轉轉遊蕩半生 <br />\n彷彿走進黑暗迷宮　 <br />\n靠渺少燈火　指引　方向 <br />\n塵風　吹熄了明路燈火 <br />\n依稀的煙霧漸飛散　令多少魂魄依賴牆壁前行 <br />\n<br />\n尋燈火　從那可　尋希望　從那可 <br />\n從黑目　來思路　從黑目　來摸索 <br />\n<br />\n由恐懼　由困惑　成習慣　成依舊 <br />\n無奈何　唯停留　無方向　唯停留 <br />\n<br />\n求變改　怕痛苦　求脫身　怕迷茫 <br />\n站立著　咬緊齒　從黑暗　思慮著　　 <br />\n衝過?　留在?　衝過?　留在? <br />\n<br />\n劃破黑暗 <br />\n<br />\n劃破漆黑中的驚慌　踏進思憶中的曙光 <br />\n燻黑卻已久的瞳孔　捉不到熾熱的花火 <br />\n<br />\n躺進盼望中的被窩　翻開作掩護的雙臂 <br />\n張開那恐懼的眼睛　戰勝煩擾已久的心魔"},{"pid":"69f81c6fb0e8db8892e937152a889698ce81dc75","tid":100498,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:39:02.000Z","msg":"明年今日？"},{"pid":"1f94d4aa713b6924ae991bb11209c38cd356bafe","tid":100498,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明年今日？</blockquote><br />\n永遠在床上發夢 餘生都不會再悲哀"},{"pid":"52013f6c2c43c90ee927cbbea59c335f1a81ee1a","tid":100498,"uid":2864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"門生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時先肯出新碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeaaf1fc61300416a2f60eee3f305ae1a877c53","tid":100498,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>門生<img src=\"/assets/f